#. <section class="sutta" id="sn14.14"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn14.14:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 14"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 14"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn14.14:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 14. Hīnādhimuttikasutta → hīnādhimutti (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn14.14:0.3"
msgid "14. Hīnādhimuttikasutta"
msgstr "14. Believers in Low Things"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn14.14:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

#. VAR: Dhātusova → dhātuso (si, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn14.14:1.2"
msgid "“Dhātusova, bhikkhave, sattā saṃsandanti samenti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, sentient beings come together and converge because of an "
"element."

msgctxt "sn14.14:1.3"
msgid "Hīnādhimuttikā hīnādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;"
msgstr ""
"Those who believe in low things come together and converge with those who "
"believe in low things."

msgctxt "sn14.14:1.4"
msgid "kalyāṇādhimuttikā kalyāṇādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti."
msgstr ""
"Those who believe in good things come together and converge with those who "
"believe in good things."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: kho → khosaddo bj, s1-3, km, pts1-2 potthakesu
msgctxt "sn14.14:2.1"
msgid "Atītampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṃ dhātusova sattā saṃsandiṃsu samiṃsu."
msgstr ""
"In the past, too, sentient beings came together and converged because of an "
"element. …"

msgctxt "sn14.14:2.2"
msgid "Hīnādhimuttikā hīnādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandiṃsu samiṃsu;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn14.14:2.3"
msgid "kalyāṇādhimuttikā kalyāṇādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandiṃsu samiṃsu."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: kho → khosaddo bj, s1-3, km, pts1-2 potthakesu
msgctxt "sn14.14:3.1"
msgid ""
"Anāgatampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṃ dhātusova sattā saṃsandissanti "
"samessanti."
msgstr ""
"In the future, too, sentient beings will come together and converge because "
"of an element. …"

msgctxt "sn14.14:3.2"
msgid "Hīnādhimuttikā hīnādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandissanti samessanti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn14.14:3.3"
msgid ""
"kalyāṇādhimuttikā kalyāṇādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandissanti samessanti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.155"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: kho → khosaddo bj, s1-3, km, pts1-2 potthakesu
msgctxt "sn14.14:4.1"
msgid ""
"Etarahipi kho, bhikkhave, paccuppannaṃ addhānaṃ dhātusova sattā saṃsandanti "
"samenti."
msgstr ""
"At present, too, sentient beings come together and converge because of an "
"element."

msgctxt "sn14.14:4.2"
msgid "Hīnādhimuttikā hīnādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti;"
msgstr ""
"Those who believe in low things come together and converge with those who "
"believe in low things."

msgctxt "sn14.14:4.3"
msgid "kalyāṇādhimuttikā kalyāṇādhimuttikehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samentī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Those who believe in good things come together and converge with those who "
"believe in good things.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn14.14:4.4"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
